reviewText: An awesome book for plant food lovers.

Love this DVD Pressure Cooking, Afresh Look: Delicious Dishes in Minutes. Recipes are easy and I felt empowered to actually try some of them.  Yum.  I was afraid of my pressure cooker until I read Jill's book and watched the DVD.  Actually I liked her Pressure cooking book better than the DVD, but books are more of a preference for me than a DVD.
